data.description: Welcome home to this bright and charming rambler! With nearly 1700 square feet, this house has it all with an open floor plan, huge kitchen with prep island, stainless steel appliances, oversized primary suite and bonus room. Stay warm and cozy with the wood burning pellet stove during the colder seasons and the surrounding trees offer privacy and shade during the hot days. Plus a 24x24 shop and storage shed in the back. Fully fenced back yard, No HOA's, and RV parking. Conveniently located in a quiet neighborhood yet only a few minutes to parks, shopping, I-5, and more.
